                                              class="- topic/entry ">
														                            <p class="- topic/p ">Contractor has exceeded many of the significant award-fee criteria and has met overall cost, schedule, and technical performance requirements of the contract in the aggregate as defined and measured against the criteria in the award-fee plan for the award-fee evaluation period.</p>
													                          </entry>
												                        </row>
