											                      </tbody>
										                    </tgroup>
									                  </table>
								                </li>
								                <li class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p id="d1009e367" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(v)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                    Prohibit earning any award fee when a contractor’s overall cost, schedule, and technical performance in the aggregate is below satisfactory;</p>
								                </li>
								                <li class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p id="d1009e377" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(vi)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                    Provide for evaluation period(s) to be conducted at stated intervals during the contract period of performance so that the contractor will periodically be informed of the quality of its performance and the areas in which improvement is expected (<i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">e.g.</i> six months, nine months, twelve months, or at specific milestones); and</p>
								                </li>
								                <li class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p id="d1009e389" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(vii)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                    Define the total award-fee pool amount and how this amount is allocated across each evaluation period.</p>
								                </li>
								                <li class="- topic/li ">
									                  <ol id="d995e392" class="- topic/ol ">
										                    <li class="- topic/li ">
											                      <p id="d1009e402" class="- topic/p ">
                                    <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(A)</ph>
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
												                        
												                        <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Rollover of unearned award fee</i>. The use of rollover of unearned award fee is prohibited.</p>
										                    </li>
										                    <li class="- topic/li ">
											                      <p id="d1009e414" class="- topic/p ">
                                    <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(B)</ph>
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
												                        
												                        <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Limitations</i>. No award-fee contract shall be awarded unless-</p>
											                      <ol id="d995e417" class="- topic/ol ">
												                        <li class="- topic/li ">
													                          <p id="d1009e427" class="- topic/p ">
                                          <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                                          
                                          
                                          
                                          
                                          
                                          
                                          
                                          
                                          
                                          
                                          
														                            All of the limitations in <xref href="FAR-i1104650.dita#i1104650"
                                                base="i1104650"
                                                outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                                                class="- topic/xref ">16.301-3</xref>, that are applicable to cost-reimbursement contracts only, are complied with;</p>
												                        </li>
												                        <li class="- topic/li ">
													                          <p id="d1009e439" class="- topic/p ">
                                          <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                                          
                                          
                                          
                                          
                                          
                                          
                                          
                                          
                                          
                                          
                                          
														                            An award-fee plan is completed in accordance with the requirements in <xref href="#i1104345"
                                                base="i1104345"
                                                outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                                                class="- topic/xref ">16.401</xref>(e)(3); and</p>
												                        </li>
												                        <li class="- topic/li ">
													                          <p id="d1009e451" class="- topic/p ">
                                          <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                                          
                                          
                                          
                                          
                                          
                                          
                                          
                                          
                                          
                                          
                                          
														                            A determination and finding is completed in accordance with <xref href="#i1104345"
                                                base="i1104345"
                                                outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                                                class="- topic/xref ">16.401</xref>(d) addressing all of the suitability items in <xref href="#i1104345"
                                                base="i1104345"
                                                outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                                                class="- topic/xref ">16.401</xref>(e)(1).</p>
												                        </li>
											                      </ol>
										                    </li>
									                  </ol>
								                </li>
							              </ol>
						            </li>
